- [woman] Hi, Alex.

19
00:00:56,974 --> 00:01:00,512
[man] So, what about it? Why do
So many people write about the fall?

20
00:01:00,602 --> 00:01:04,220
[woman] Well, I think it's seen
as the beginning of the end, really.

21
00:01:04,314 --> 00:01:08,182
If the year is a life, then September,
the beginning of fall,

22
00:01:08,277 --> 00:01:11,611
is when the bloom is off the rose
and things start to die.

23
00:01:11,697 --> 00:01:15,691
It's a melancholy month and maybe
because of that, quite beautiful.

24
00:01:15,784 --> 00:01:17,741
